# M7 — Low-Level Primitives & Systems Toolkit

**25+ years of battle-tested, bloat-free JavaScript and systems tools**  
Now open-sourcing the core primitives that power real production systems.

Focus: Minimal, composable building blocks — DOM mastery, event/observation, timing, logging, tree inspection, networking, and secure daemons.  
No frameworks. No dependencies where possible. Performance and clarity first.

**Current status**  
- `m7-js` core library: v0.98 live (most primitives online)  
- v1.0 release targeted shortly — full docs, npm packages, examples

