## JavaScript Ecosystem (m7-js)

### Core Library: m7-js.lib.*
The heart of M7 — modular primitives under `lib.primitive.*` namespace (dashes → dots in logical path).

- **lib.primitive.dom.eventdelegator**  
  [m7-js-lib-primitive-dom-eventdelegator](https://github.com/linearblade/m7-js-lib-primitive-dom-eventdelegator)  
  Selector-aware DOM event delegation primitive built on native bubbling/capture. Routes events through explicit selectors and policies — no ad-hoc logic.

- **lib.primitive.dom.changeobserver**  
  [m7-js-lib-primitive-dom-changeobserver](https://github.com/linearblade/m7-js-lib-primitive-dom-changeobserver)  
  Selector-aware DOM change reporting primitive using MutationObserver. Tracks membership transitions (added/removed/changed/changeAway) in batches — reports facts, imposes no behavior.

- **lib.primitive.log**  
  [m7-js-lib-primitive-log](https://github.com/linearblade/m7-js-lib-primitive-log)  
  (No description yet — lightweight logging primitive)

- **lib.primitive.interval**  
  [m7-js-lib-interval](https://github.com/linearblade/m7-js-lib-interval)  
  Precise, cancelable timers & schedulers

- **lib.tree**  
  [m7-js-lib-tree](https://github.com/linearblade/m7-js-lib-tree)  
  Runtime JavaScript object tree inspector and console for exploring large APIs and object graphs. Great for debugging massive/undocumented structures.

- **lib.098**  
  [m7-js-lib-098](https://github.com/linearblade/m7-js-lib-098)  
  (No description yet — experimental/misc primitive)

